Privacy Policy for Encroffline

This Privacy Policy describes how Encroffline ("we", "us", or "our") collects, uses, and shares information when you use our Encroffline application (the "App"). By using the App, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.

Information Collection and Use

Encroffline is an offline PGP chat application that does not require any internet connection for its functionality. We emphasize that Encroffline operates entirely offline and does not collect any personal information from users through the App. All communication within the App is encrypted using PGP (Pretty Good Privacy) encryption, ensuring the privacy and security of your messages.

Data Security

We take data security seriously. Encroffline employs state-of-the-art encryption methods to secure all communications and data stored within the App. Your messages and personal information are encrypted using PGP encryption, ensuring that only you and your intended recipient can access them.

Disclosure of Information

We do not disclose any personal information collected through the App to third parties. Since Encroffline is offline and does not collect any data, your messages and personal data remain private and inaccessible to anyone except you and your chosen recipients.

Demo Version and Paid Version

Encroffline offers both a demo version and a paid version. Please note that these versions differ in functionality. The demo version may have limited features compared to the paid version. Users should review the features of each version before making a purchase decision.

Data Retention

Encroffline does not retain any message data on our servers. All messages are stored locally on your device and are encrypted using PGP encryption. You have full control over the retention and deletion of your messages within the App.

Children's Privacy

Encroffline is not intended for use by children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you are a parent or guardian and become aware that your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us so that we can take appropriate action.

Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes to this policy will be reflected in the updated version of the App. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.
